divs: Sighting Detailswas come back from a friends house and was watching the coburg hill me and my family watched a campfire just appear out of nowhere and then it move about 20 feet and just stop.then something shot out from the right side and just took off.that was it for about 20 mins and then this rainbow light just appears to the left of the campfire light and it slowly heads over to it kind of at a angle.and then the light is gone within a matter of a few seconds poof gone.light the light was still there when we got home so i called the police and reported what I had seen.
